**Novalad** is an AI-powered platform that transforms chaotic, unstructured files‚Äîsuch as PDFs and PowerPoints‚Äîinto beautifully organized, machine-readable data üí°. Designed for developers, data teams, and enterprises, Novalad efficiently handles complex layouts, tables, graphs, and multi-format data using a multi-model, map-reduce approach üß©.

[View Novalad Extraction Result](https://www.novalad.ai/comparision.html)


